\int_{\gamma} ds = \int_{\gamma} \frac{2 \left| dz \right|}{1 + \left| z \right|^{2}} = \int_{\gamma} \frac{2 \sqrt{dx^2 + dy^2}}{1 + x^2 + y^2} = \int_a^b \frac{2 \sqrt{x'(t)^2 + y'(t)^2}}{1 + x(t)^2 + y(t)^2} dt
